---
---
<section id="top" class="hero">
  <div class="hero-bg" id="heroBg"></div>
  <div class="hero-inner">
    <span class="eyebrow mono">SELF ROASTED / BROOKLYN STYLE / SINCE 2014</span>
    <h1>ROASTED<br>IN THE<br><span class="outline">RAW.</span></h1>
    <p class="hero-sub">配管とレンガがむき出しの焙煎所併設カフェ。豆の個性を焼き切らず、素材の力をそのまま抽出する。ここはコーヒー好きが集まる、ブルックリンの裏路地のような場所。</p>
    <div class="btn-row">
      <a href="#menu" class="btn solid">View Menu</a>
      <a href="#access" class="btn outline">Find Us</a>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="hero-float">
    <div class="num">7,300+</div>
    <div class="label">CUPS ROASTED / MONTH</div>
  </div>
  <div class="scroll-cue"><div class="scroll-line"></div>SCROLL</div>
</section>

<div class="marquee-band">
  <div class="marquee-track">
    <span>SINGLE ORIGIN</span><span class="solid">DIRECT TRADE</span><span>SMALL BATCH</span><span class="solid">DRUM ROASTED</span><span>BROOKLYN STYLE</span>
    <span>SINGLE ORIGIN</span><span class="solid">DIRECT TRADE</span><span>SMALL BATCH</span><span class="solid">DRUM ROASTED</span><span>BROOKLYN STYLE</span>
  </div>
</div>

<style>
  /* hero */
  .hero { min-height: 100vh; position: relative; display: flex; align-items: center; padding-top: 120px; overflow: hidden; }
  .hero-bg {
    position: absolute; inset: -10%; /* GSAPパララックスのために少し大きく */
    background: url('/images/hero.jpg') center 30%/cover no-repeat;
    will-change: transform;
  }
  .hero-bg::after {
    content: ""; position: absolute; inset: 0;
    background: linear-gradient(180deg, rgba(10,9,8,0.55) 0%, rgba(10,9,8,0.97) 92%);
  }
  .hero-inner { position: relative; z-index: 2; max-width: 1240px; margin: 0 auto; width: 100%; padding: 0 32px; }
  .eyebrow { font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace; font-size: 12px; letter-spacing: 0.25em; color: var(--copper); margin-bottom: 22px; display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 12px; }
  .eyebrow::before { content: ""; width: 32px; height: 1px; background: var(--copper); }
  .hero h1 { font-size: clamp(52px, 11vw, 168px); color: var(--cream); margin-bottom: 6px; }
  .hero h1 .outline { color: transparent; -webkit-text-stroke: 2px var(--cream); }
  .hero-sub { max-width: 520px; color: var(--cream-dim); font-size: 17px; margin: 26px 0 38px; }
  .btn-row { display: flex; gap: 16px; flex-wrap: wrap; }
  .btn { display: inline-block; padding: 16px 32px; font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace; font-size: 13px; letter-spacing: 0.1em; text-transform: uppercase; border: 1px solid var(--cream); transition: all .3s; position: relative; overflow: hidden; }
  .btn.solid { background: var(--brick-bright); border-color: var(--brick-bright); color: var(--black); font-weight: 700; }
  .btn.solid:hover { background: var(--cream); border-color: var(--cream); }
  .btn.outline { background: transparent; }
  .btn.outline:hover { background: var(--cream); color: var(--black); }

  .hero-float {
    position: absolute; right: 6%; bottom: 14%; z-index: 3;
    background: rgba(10,9,8,0.7); backdrop-filter: blur(6px);
    border: 1px solid var(--line-strong); padding: 22px 26px; max-width: 220px;
    animation: float 5s ease-in-out infinite;
  }
  @keyframes float { 0%, 100% { transform: translateY(0); } 50% { transform: translateY(-10px); } }
  .hero-float .num { font-family: 'Anton', sans-serif; font-size: 38px; color: var(--copper); }
  .hero-float .label { font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace; font-size: 10px; color: var(--ash); letter-spacing: 0.08em; margin-top: 4px; }
  @media (max-width: 900px) { .hero-float { display: none; } }

  .scroll-cue { position: absolute; bottom: 36px; left: 32px; z-index: 3; display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 10px; font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace; font-size: 10px; color: var(--ash); letter-spacing: 0.15em; }
  .scroll-line { width: 1px; height: 36px; background: var(--ash); position: relative; overflow: hidden; }
  .scroll-line::after { content: ""; position: absolute; top: -100%; left: 0; width: 100%; height: 100%; background: var(--copper); animation: scrolldrop 1.8s ease-in-out infinite; }
  @keyframes scrolldrop { to { top: 100%; } }

  /* marquee band */
  .marquee-band { border-bottom: 1px solid var(--line); border-top: 1px solid var(--line); overflow: hidden; padding: 22px 0; background: var(--charcoal); }
  .marquee-track { display: inline-flex; white-space: nowrap; animation: marquee 22s linear infinite; }
  .marquee-track span { font-family: 'Anton', sans-serif; font-size: 34px; padding: 0 28px; color: transparent; -webkit-text-stroke: 1px var(--line-strong); text-transform: uppercase; }
  .marquee-track span.solid { -webkit-text-stroke: 0; color: var(--copper); }
  @keyframes marquee { from { transform: translateX(0); } to { transform: translateX(-50%); } }
</style>
